desc: Raises Atk parameter limits to 150000, 100% boost to Atk and boosts critical hit rate of Fire types, greatly boosts critical damage & negates critical damage

dictionary.lore: A wing of fiery, barely-bound elemental power, it can sear the flesh of those careless enough to handle it improperly. Attuning to it grants a great boost in magical energy...and a glimpse of something greater.

name: Wildfire Wing
